%e5%b0%8f%2c629%2c20221005%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"STEV,111,店小,629,20221005,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"店小","JNO":"629","JDATE":"20221005","JTITLE":"給付分期付款買賣價金"}